      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――LizNoir北海道ライブツアー　出発前",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Before Departing for LizNoir's Hokkaido Live Tour",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5006.666626900001,
          "startTime": 5.0066666269
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_airport-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "airport-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_01-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "パティスリー・ウフーフさんの\n限定、激・たまごプリンは外せませんし～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can’t forget the limited-edition‚\nsuper egg pudding from Pâtisserie Oeuf~‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_airport-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "airport-00-noon",
      "startTime": 7.5371199846
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_01-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "ウフーフさんと同じ並びにある名店\nラ・ラーラさんの限定、濃過ぎるミルクプリンも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And then there’s the limited-edition‚\nextra-rich milk pudding from the famous shop La・LaーLa‚ which is in the same row as Oeuf…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.7666665395,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "こころ、そんなにスマホにかじりついて\n何をしてるんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kokoro‚ what are you doing glued\nto your phone like that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_airport-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "airport-00-noon",
      "startTime": 17.9193876823
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_01-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "あ、{user}さん、お疲れ様です～\n今はSNSで、北海道のプリンの名店をチェック中です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ hello {user}-san~!\nI’m checking out famous pudding places in Hokkaido on social media!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.2099998157,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "プリン？　なんで北海道に行くのにわざわざ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Pudding? Why are you looking that up when we’re going to Hokkaido…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.7459410589,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_airport-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "airport-00-noon",
      "startTime": 29.3097283444
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_01-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "それ、本気で言ってます？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you serious?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.3097283444,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_airport-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "airport-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.4816774131
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_01-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "仕方ありませんね～。ヒントをあげましょう。もちろん\nプリンの材料は知っていますよね。常識ですよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Guess I’ll have to give you a hint. Of course‚\nyou know the ingredients for pudding‚ right? It’s common sense‚ isn’t it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.6404527506,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_01-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "そうです、牛乳、そして卵です\n酪農の大地北海道と言えば、牛乳じゃないですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s right‚ milk and eggs!\nThe dairy land of Hokkaido… you think of milk‚ right?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.0404527506,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_airport-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "airport-00-noon",
      "startTime": 50.252237932
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_01-kkr007.m4a",
      "text": "その上北海道は卵の生産量も秘かに凄いんですよ～\nこれでプリンを買わずして何を買うと？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "On top of that‚ Hokkaido’s egg production is secretly amazing~!\nWhat else would you buy there?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_01-kkr008.m4a",
      "text": "北海道の材料を前面に押し出しているプリンとなれば\n現地で食べるのが礼儀ですよ～。それに――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If it’s a pudding made with Hokkaido ingredients‚\nit’s only polite to eat it there~. And――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.5737807435,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_airport-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "airport-00-noon",
      "startTime": 65.2607484263
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "こ、こころのプリンに対する情熱はよく分かった\nじゃ、俺はこれで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "K-Kokoro‚ I get your passion for pudding.\nWell‚ I’m going to…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.8333333335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_airport-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "airport-00-noon",
      "startTime": 70.5564877909
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_01-kkr009.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと、まだ話は終わってませんよー！\nこころとプリンへの愛が足りてないんじゃないですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ hold on‚ I’m not done talking!\nDon’t you have enough love for me and pudding?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.3695262117,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_01-kkr010.m4a",
      "text": "そうだ！　飛行機に乗るまで、少し時間がありますし\nこころと一緒にプリンのお勉強をしましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know! We have some time before we board the plane‚\nso let’s study pudding together!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.002859545,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_airport-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "airport-00-noon",
      "startTime": 84.2548557044
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "あ、あぁ……それは後でな\n随分浮かれてるけど、ライブの準備は大丈夫なのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "U-Uh… maybe later.\nYou seem pretty excited. But are you sure you’re ready for the live?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.7000000002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_01-kkr011.m4a",
      "text": "愚問ですね～。セトリもMCのネタもバッチリです\nリズノワのセンター、この赤崎こころに任せて下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s a silly question~. The setlist and MC parts are all perfect!\nYou can leave it to LizNoir’s center‚ Akazaki Kokoro!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.5419526261,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 12466.663741999995,
          "startTime": 109.0086163681
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_airport-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "airport-00-noon",
      "startTime": 96.5419526261
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_01-kkr012.m4a",
      "text": "北の大地に、こころの名前とスマイルを刻んでみせます\n……って、あそこに見えるは空港限定プリン！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ll etch my name and smile onto the northern lands!\n…Wait‚ is that an airport-limited edition pudding?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.2086192927,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_airport-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "airport-00-noon",
      "startTime": 108.6795281489
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_airport-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "airport-00-noon",
      "startTime": 110.3155167024
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "さすがに、はしゃぎ過ぎな気もするけど……\nまぁ、ライブの準備も出来てるなら大丈夫か",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You seem a little too excited…\nWell‚ I guess it’s fine if you’re prepared for the live.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.7999989829,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ライブでミクとコラボすることが決まった翌日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The Day After the Miku Collaboration for the Live Was Decided",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.8800292413,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 119.9800292413
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 119.9800292413
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_01-kkr013.m4a",
      "text": "さ、ささささ、さ、寒いです……\nもうダメです……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-It’s s-s-so c-cold…\nI-I can’t go on anymore…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.339797481,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 127.4772215446
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_01-kkr014.m4a",
      "text": "寒過ぎて、だんだん眠く……\nあぁ、天使さんがこころを迎えに来てくれてる……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s so cold‚ I’m getting sleepy…\nAhh‚ an angel has come to take me away…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.9398015501,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 136.833909599
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "……こころ、ホテルの前で何をやってるんだ？\nスタジオに練習に行ったんじゃなかったのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Kokoro‚ what are you doing in front of the hotel?\nDidn’t you go to the studio to practice?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.5999979657,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 143.3712482055
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_01-kkr015.m4a",
      "text": "うぅ……行こうとしたんです。したんですけど……\nあまりの寒さに、身動きが、ががが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "U-Ugh… I tried to go… I did…\nBut it’s so cold‚ I can’t move‚ m-m-move…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.7438058061,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "大げさだな……\nスタジオはそんなに遠くないだろ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t be dramatic…\nThe studio isn’t that far.",
